Occupy Davis is an on-going protest in Davis, California. It was formed on September 17 as part of the [[Occupy Movement]]. Beginning October 15, protestors began an occupation of the city's Central Park. <ref>[http://www.davisenterprise.com/local-news/occupy-davis-chooses-central-park-as-its-focus/ Occupy Davis chooses Central Park as its focus] </ref>
  +   +
Occupy Davis should not be confused with [[Occupy UC Davis]], the later protest movement held by students at the nearby university.
